  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/820610/extras/f05f2f525d9692661af8cb049f823e06.poster.avif?t=1667267979\" width=624 height=212 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/820610/extras/f05f2f525d9692661af8cb049f823e06.webm?t=1667267979\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/820610/extras/f05f2f525d9692661af8cb049f823e06.mp4?t=1667267979\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> <br><br>The kingdom is under attack and the princess has been taken! <br>Can our four mages assume the responsibility of Guardian and reinvigorate the ages of the mages?<br><br>-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------<br> <h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > Main Features </h2><br>■ Third-person shooter beat 'em up game with  RPG and Rogue-Lite elements.<br>■ 4 kinds of mages, each with its own characteristics.<br>■ 20+ wands, each wand has different maigc skill.<br>■ Skill tree, unlocking your powerful magic.<br>■ Randomly generated dungeons.<br>■ 7 chapters，38 stages，14 boss fights.<br>■ Up to 4 local player co-op, as well as a single-player option.<br>■ Supports both mouse/keyboard and Xbox gamepad.<br><br>-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >whom do you like?</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/820610/extras/bbddff18e8411c44527d8eae3b336996.avif?t=1667267979\" width=620 height=162 /></span><br><br>4 cute mages each with its own characteristics.<br>Some attacks are strong, some hit wide, some are fast, and some can heal. <br><br>How about our fire mage? Good?<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/820610/extras/5a751fa4401a92aa246871fec48bd708.poster.avif?t=1667267979\" width=624 height=212 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/820610/extras/5a751fa4401a92aa246871fec48bd708.webm?t=1667267979\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/820610/extras/5a751fa4401a92aa246871fec48bd708.mp4?t=1667267979\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Ice mages refuses to accept.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/820610/extras/98c58c1fc45d0a9c705e52901ffa0015.poster.avif?t=1667267979\" width=624 height=212 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/820610/extras/98c58c1fc45d0a9c705e52901ffa0015.webm?t=1667267979\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/820610/extras/98c58c1fc45d0a9c705e52901ffa0015.mp4?t=1667267979\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>The mage of Nature is roaring: I can buy one get one!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/820610/extras/c977d7adae2ca271e822731b7ff6fb53.poster.avif?t=1667267979\" width=624 height=212 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/820610/extras/c977d7adae2ca271e822731b7ff6fb53.webm?t=1667267979\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/820610/extras/c977d7adae2ca271e822731b7ff6fb53.mp4?t=1667267979\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>The Lightning mage laugh without saying, \"Trust me, I can make everything easy\".<br><span class=